scenes.description: Kiryu Coco interacts with the members of hololive English (Myth) during her graduation stream.

subtitles.english: EN

subtitles.original: はい！
subtitles.english: Okay!

subtitles.original: ではここからは、ホロライブ EN の後輩どもに来てもらいましたよ！
subtitles.english: Now I've got the members of hololive English here!

subtitles.original: 皆さん！Thank you for coming to
subtitles.english: Guys! Thank you for coming to

subtitles.original: my 桐生会事務所！
subtitles.english: my Kiryu Group Headquarters!

subtitles.original: hololive English の皆、イエーイ！

subtitles.original: Hello!

subtitles.original: Guys! Thank you for coming to my graduation stream!
subtitles.english: Guys! Thank you for coming to my graduation stream!

subtitles.original: Oh, don't feel sad!
subtitles.english: Oh, don't feel sad!

subtitles.original: Of course! Of course!
subtitles.english: Of course! Of course!

subtitles.original: Any time for you, Senpai.
subtitles.english: Any time for you, Senpai.

subtitles.original: ありがと、来てくれて。
subtitles.english: Thanks for being here!

subtitles.original: 今日はね、あの私の、え、卒業ということで、色々とね...
subtitles.english: Today, well, it's my graduation.

subtitles.original: ...あの後輩なんでね、ちょっと私と一緒に過ごす時間は皆さんよりかは少なくなってしまいましたけど...
subtitles.english: And my juniors here, well, haven't had as much time with me as everyone else,

subtitles.original: ...色んな印象とかあったら聞いていこうかなと思います。
subtitles.english: but I'd like to hear what your memories of me are like.

subtitles.original: So guys! Well, you guys... as you guys know, I am graduating, but umm...
subtitles.english: So guys! Well, you guys... as you guys know, I am graduating, but umm...

subtitles.original: What did you guys think about Kiryu Coco?
subtitles.english: What did you guys think about Kiryu Coco?

subtitles.original: You have any memories?
subtitles.english: You have any memories?

subtitles.original: Iconic!
subtitles.english: Iconic!

subtitles.original: Iconic?
subtitles.english: Iconic?

subtitles.original: An absolute icon.
subtitles.english: An absolute icon.

subtitles.original: Really? Was I?
subtitles.english: Really? Was I?

subtitles.original: And literally the reason we are here.
subtitles.english: And literally the reason we are here.

subtitles.original: We wouldn't be here without you, Senpai. We freakin' love you!
subtitles.english: We wouldn't be here without you, Senpai. We freakin' love you!

subtitles.original: Oh god, really?
subtitles.english: Oh god, really?

subtitles.original: How about you, Kiara-chan?
subtitles.english: How about you, Kiara-chan?

subtitles.original: Uh, in the beginning, I thought that... when I saw your debut stream...
subtitles.english: Uh, in the beginning, I thought that... when I saw your debut stream...

subtitles.original: I thought that you were a really creative and funny dragon.
subtitles.english: I thought that you were a really creative and funny dragon.

subtitles.original: But also an insanely hard worker from the beginning, because you did stuff like Morning Coco.
subtitles.english: But also an insanely hard worker from the beginning, because you did stuff like Morning Coco.

subtitles.original: And I thought that was like... anything you did was really interesting.
subtitles.english: And I thought that was like... anything you did was really interesting.

subtitles.original: But one thing that I was worried about is if it's not difficult to speak when your tongue is always sticking out!
subtitles.english: But one thing that I was worried about is if it's not difficult to speak when your tongue is always sticking out!

subtitles.original: True!
subtitles.english: True!

subtitles.original: At that time my mouth was like always open, I know! I remember.
subtitles.english: At that time my mouth was like always open, I know! I remember.

subtitles.original: Yeah!
subtitles.english: Yeah!

subtitles.original: And my tongue was always sticking out, and I was...
subtitles.english: And my tongue was always sticking out, and I was...

subtitles.original: It looked like I was speaking with my tongue out always. It was like...
subtitles.english: It looked like I was speaking with my tongue out always. It was like...

subtitles.original: (Coco speaking in tongue)
subtitles.english: (Coco speaking in tongue)

subtitles.original: Yeah!
subtitles.english: Yeah!

subtitles.original: Plus, I kinda sounded like I was like—you know, I had the... well, I do right now, but a nasal voice.
subtitles.english: Plus, I kinda sounded like I was like—you know, I had the... well, I do right now, but a nasal voice.

subtitles.original: It kinda really looked like I was really talking with my tongue out.
subtitles.english: It kinda really looked like I was really talking with my tongue out.

subtitles.original: But I wasn't! I wasn't! It just looked like that.
subtitles.english: But I wasn't! I wasn't! It just looked like that.

subtitles.english: How about you, Ina-chan?

subtitles.original: Ina-chan! Thank you for coming!
subtitles.english: Ina-chan! Thank you for coming!

subtitles.original: Thank you for having us!
subtitles.english: Thank you for having us!

subtitles.original: I know we didn't have much time to interact with each other, but, you know...
subtitles.english: I know we didn't have much time to interact with each other, but, you know...

subtitles.original: We're BFFs, right?
subtitles.english: We're BFFs, right?

subtitles.original: Yeah.
subtitles.english: Yeah.

subtitles.original: Well... how could I forget your legendary 3D debut stream?
subtitles.english: Well... how could I forget your legendary 3D debut stream?

subtitles.original: Your dance moves just... wow. Captivating. Legendary.
subtitles.english: Your dance moves just... wow. Captivating. Legendary.

subtitles.original: Aw, thank you! Thank you so much!
subtitles.english: Aw, thank you! Thank you so much!

subtitles.english: They all watch my streams more than I thought. That makes me happy!

subtitles.original: Amelia! Thank you for coming!
subtitles.english: Amelia! Thank you for coming!

subtitles.original: Thank you for having me!
subtitles.english: Thank you for having me!

subtitles.english: Now that Ina mentioned your birthday stream, I remember we were all watching your 3D debut,

subtitles.english: You did a flip and we were like, "Did she just do a flip? What the hell?!"

subtitles.english: I can't do that. I can't even do a handstand. Damn!

subtitles.english: Yeah, I wanted to dance with you guys! I wanted to dance with you guys!
